texts.text: Runecraft's wiki has moved to its own platform.
Visit us at https://runecraft.wiki/ for the official wiki, and the most up to date changes to Runecraft.

The Runecraft team would like to extend our sincerest thank yous to the Gamepedia team, and everyone involved over the years for giving us a wonderful place to call home until now. We hope there's no ill-feelings on any front. We just felt that for the future of our project it was the best move we could have made. Thank you again for many great years.
